            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "To reduce errors in the measurement of the polarization",
                "of the beam by changes in the beam profile at the in-",
                "beam polarimeter target position, a spot target was",
                "used consisting of a 100-mg/cm**2 CH(2) foil with a",
                "diameter of 2-mm placed on a 4-mum thin aluminum",
                "backing."
              ]
            }
          ],
